    "body": "> it was written 5 times when I was on forge 0.2.0 (48d5d79 2022-09-01T00:10:22.933552Z), and 6 times once I bumped to forge 0.2.0 (4b9cca1 2022-09-03T00:09:38.998187Z)\r\n\r\nweird, both resulted in 5 for me\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\ntracked the root cause of this behaviour down to this:\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/1c415857dd7b617190834dbcb361506f6143fed4/cli/src/cmd/forge/script/runner.rs#L217-L233\r\n\r\nas a solution, we can add something like `commit: bool` to the cheatcodes config:\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/1c415857dd7b617190834dbcb361506f6143fed4/evm/src/executor/inspector/cheatcodes/config.rs#L19\r\n, so all file write operations will be executed only on the last committing call",
